e item to be active at a time."},"74":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-27","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#controlled","content":"Use `selectedKeys` and `onSelectionChange` to fully control selection from parent state.\n`onSelectionChange` receives a `Set<string>` containing the `id` values of the selected items."},"75":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-28","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#sizes","content":"Two sizes are available: `sm` and `md` (default)."},"76":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-29","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#icon--text","content":"Items can include an `Icon` alongside text for added visual context."},"77":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-30","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#icon-only","content":"For compact layouts, items can contain only icons. Padding adjusts automatically to keep the button square — no extra prop required. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only item so screen readers can identify the action."},"78":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-31","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#with-dropdown","content":"Use a `MenuTrigger` inside a `ButtonGroup` when one of the actions has sub-options."},"79":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-32","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#rtl-direction","content":"The button group follows the current layout direction (LTR or RTL). Direction is detected automatically from the browser or system settings via RAC's `I18nProvider`."},"80":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-33","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#disabled-states","content":"Disable the entire group with `isDisabled` on the container, or disable individual items with `isDisabled` on specific `ButtonGroupItem` elements."},"81":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-34","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Key"},"82":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-35","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Action"},"83":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-36","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Tab**"},"84":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-37","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Moves focus to/from the button group (single tab stop)"},"85":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-38","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Arrow Left / Right**"},"86":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-39","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus between items (RAC automatically reverses in RTL)"},"87":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-40","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Space / Enter**"},"88":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-41","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Toggle the focused item"},"89":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-42","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Home**"},"90":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-43","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the first item"},"91":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-44","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"**End**"},"92":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-45","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the last item"},"93":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-46","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"single\"` → `role=\"radiogroup\"` on container, `role=\"radio\"` + `aria-checked` per item"},"94":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-47","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"multiple\"` → `role=\"toolbar\"` on container, `role=\"button\"` + `aria-pressed` per item"},"95":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-48","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#aria-support","content":"`aria-label` (or `aria-labelledby`) is required on the group container"},"96":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-49","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#aria-support","content":"Icon-only items require `aria-label` on each `ButtonGroupItem`"},"97":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-50","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-to-use","content":"**Grouped contextual actions** — two or more closely related actions that belong together (e.g. Bold / Italic / Underline, Align Left / Center / Right)."},"98":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-51","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-to-use","content":"**Compact action grouping** — related actions in space-constrained layouts (e.g. Undo / Redo, Zoom In / Out / Reset)."},"99":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-52","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-to-use","content":"**Multi-select scenarios** — when users need to select multiple options simultaneously."},"100":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-53","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-not-to-use","content":"**Unrelated actions** — buttons that perform disconnected tasks without shared context."},"101":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-54","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-not-to-use","content":"**Too many options** — more than 5 choices creates cognitive overload; consider a **Select** instead."},"102":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-55","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-not-to-use","content":"**Primary vs. destructive actions** — when actions require strong visual distinction (e.g. Save vs. Delete)."},"103":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-56","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-not-to-use","content":"**Full navigation changes** — when selecting an option leads to a different page or workflow."},"104":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-57","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#when-not-to-use","content":"**View switching** — use **SegmentedController** when selecting between mutually exclusive content views (e.g. Monthly / Yearly, Overview / Details). Quick rule: if it triggers an action → ButtonGroup; if it switches between views → SegmentedController."},"105":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-58","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#keep-variants-consistent","content":"Avoid mixing different content types (text-only, icon-only, icon+text) within the same group. Mixing styles creates visual noise and makes the set feel fragmented rather than unified."},"106":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-59","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#balance-label-lengths","content":"Keep button labels of similar length. Large differences in text length cause irregular button widths and make the group appear uneven. Prefer short, concise wording."},"107":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-60","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#alignment","content":"Align the group to reflect its relationship to surrounding content:"},"108":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-61","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#alignment","content":"**Left** — when the group controls content directly below or within the same column (dashboards, tables)."},"109":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-62","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#alignment","content":"**Center** — when the group acts as a prominent toggle affecting an entire section or page."},"110":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-63","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#alignment","content":"**Right** — when the group represents utility or contextual controls (e.g. grid/list view toggle)."},"111":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-64","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#labels","content":"Use **title case**: capitalize the first letter of each word, except short prepositions."},"112":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-65","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#labels","content":"Keep labels to one or two words. Omit articles (a, an, the) and filler words."},"113":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-66","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#labels","content":"Prefer action-focused or descriptive language that communicates the option instantly."},"114":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-67","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#icon-only-items","content":"Use icon-only items only when the icon's meaning is universally recognized. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only `ButtonGroupItem`:"},"115":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-68","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#open-questions","content":"The following items need design or stakeholder input before v1 ships:"},"116":{"id":"/docs/components/button-group-69","page_id":"/docs/components/button-group","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/button-group#open-questions","content":"**Focus indicator**: Figma specifies a fixed blue (`#1976d2`) 1 px border + 2 px inset shadow. The current implementation uses `outline: 2px solid Highlight` for cross-component consistency and OS-preference respect. Confirm whether Figma's brand-blue should override this."},"117":{"id":"/docs/components/carousel","page_id":"/docs/components/carousel","type":"page","content":"Carousel","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/carousel"},"118":{"id":"/docs/components/carousel-0","page_id":"/docs/components/carousel","tags"